## Registration and start times

**Sprint Course:**

You will be randomly allocated course A or course B maps. On finishing, you will need to go to download to register your first run and your map will be quarantined until after your second sprint run

 First Sprint starts : 11.00 - 11.45.

Second Sprint starts: 11:45-12:40.

**Yellow Course:**

The yellow course is completely within the park.

Starts 11.00 - 12.40.

Shadowing: Sprint runners must not shadow yellow course competitors until after completing both parts of their sprint course, they will be able to start their second run straight after their first if required.

## Directions and parking

**Parking:** At the Hare and Hounds pub, Burnley Road, Todmorden. **OL14 8EA**

W3W: **///stewing.easy.clerk**

There is a height barrier at the car park entrance, but some roadside parking on Ashenhurst Road at the side of the pub is suitable for camper vans.

From the car park cross Burnley road using the adjacent pedestrian traffic lights and then walk 150 m towards Todmorden centre to the park entrance at W3W: **///puzzles.class.contrived**.

Start and finish are close to each other 200m into the park. The route will be taped.

 **Registration/Download: **In the park close to start.

